<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Measurements.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
Total length: male 3.96-4.31 mm (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">N</emphasis>
= 13), female 4.44-4.72 mm (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">N</emphasis>
= 8).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
The salient features of the new species include: the distal part of tegmina (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">22</figureCitation>
) with a large black patch; dorsolateral part of anal tube (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">24</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">27</figureCitation>
) with a stout finger-like process, a protrusion on the basolateral finger-like process; gonostyli (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">24</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">27</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">29</figureCitation>
) slender, inner process very narrow, apex of outer process nearly fan-shaped in lateral view.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="coloration">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Coloration.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
General color yellowish white (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–8" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 8. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 1 dorsal view 2 lateral view. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 3 dorsal view 4 lateral view. Metanigrus gremius sp. nov., male 5 dorsal view 6 lateral view. Metanigrus spinatus sp. nov., male 7 dorsal view 8 lateral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures1-8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520803" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">3</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–8" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 8. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 1 dorsal view 2 lateral view. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 3 dorsal view 4 lateral view. Metanigrus gremius sp. nov., male 5 dorsal view 6 lateral view. Metanigrus spinatus sp. nov., male 7 dorsal view 8 lateral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures1-8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520803" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">4</figureCitation>
). Frons whitish yellow. Clypeus black-brown. Vertex and pronotum white. Mesonotum brown. Eyes black. Legs yellowish brown. Tegmina semitransparent, with black patch near end. Wings hyaline. Abdomen brown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="head and thorax">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Head and thorax.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
Head (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–8" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 8. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 1 dorsal view 2 lateral view. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 3 dorsal view 4 lateral view. Metanigrus gremius sp. nov., male 5 dorsal view 6 lateral view. Metanigrus spinatus sp. nov., male 7 dorsal view 8 lateral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures1-8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520803" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">3</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">20</figureCitation>
) significantly narrower than pronotum, without median carina. Vertex shorter in middle line than wide at base (1: 1.77), with two posterolateral areolets at base not meeting medially. Frons (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">21</figureCitation>
) subrectangular, without median carina, longer in middle line than wide at widest portion (about 1.67: 1), lateral carinae with a dense row of sensory pits along outer margin. Postclypeus (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">21</figureCitation>
) with distinct median and lateral carinae. Frontoclypeal suture nearly straight. Rostrum elongate, in repose well surpassing hind-coxae. Pronotum (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">20</figureCitation>
) wider than maximum width of head (including eyes) (1.71: 1), with median carina and sinuate lateral carinae. Mesonotum (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">20</figureCitation>
) about 4.57 times longer than pronotum in midline, with distinct median carina. Tegmina (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">22</figureCitation>
) slender, longer than maximal width (2.59: 1), almost as wide at postnodal as prenodal area, veins ScP + 
<collectionCode country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile">R</collectionCode>
+ 
<collectionCode country="0" name="Mohonk Preserve, Inc.">MP</collectionCode>
with several sensory pits, 
<collectionCode country="0" name="Mohonk Preserve, Inc.">MP</collectionCode>
3 two branched; five postnodal closed cells with C1 smaller than C2, C5 placed next to C3, C4 distally displaced after the nodal line, im, r-m and anterior two-thirds of margin with white areas. Hind wing (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">23</figureCitation>
) with lateral margin notched at CuA1, CuP, and A2, more strongly at A1; A2 not reaching posterior margin. Metatibiotarsal formula: (3+5)-6-5.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="male genitalia">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Male genitalia.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
Pygofer (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">24</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">25</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">27</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">28</figureCitation>
) symmetrical, gradually narrowed towards apex, with sinuate anterior and posterior margins. Pygopher with internal sulcus, with slightly curved lateral margins in ventral view. Anal tube (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">24</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">27</figureCitation>
) in lateral view, hand-shaped, anal style slender, lateral lobes distally shorter than anal style, dorsolateral part with a stout finger-like process, a protrusion on the basolateral finger-like process. Aedeagus (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">24</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">26</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 20–30" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 20 - 30. Metanigrus guttatus sp. nov., male 20 head and thorax, dorsal view 21 frons, ventral view 22 tegmina 23 Wing 24, 27 pygofer, lateral view 25, 28 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 26 aedeagus, left lateral view 29 gonostyli, dorsal view 30 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures20-30" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520805" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">27</figureCitation>
, 
